Flapjacks!

03:54.434 --> 03:57.301
Out of the frying pan!

03:58.705 --> 04:02.266
Yuck! All right, uh,
let's get started on lunch.

04:02.375 --> 04:06.243
- And-Wait. Where's Lenny?
- <i>Hello?</i>

04:06.346 --> 04:09.247
Can anybody hear me?

04:09.349 --> 04:11.249
I think I found a way out.

04:11.351 --> 04:13.945
It's not pretty, but it'll do.

04:17.156 --> 04:19.454
<i>All right, look, we gotta</i>
<i>do something about Bunyan.</i>

04:19.559 --> 04:21.754
