Laura Ingalls Wilder.

04:31.437 --> 04:33.564
Yeah, that's a great idea!

04:33.673 --> 04:37.040
Hmm.

04:37.143 --> 04:39.543
Uh, hey, Paulie?

04:39.646 --> 04:42.410
What say we buy you a beer?

04:47.053 --> 04:50.853
Aw, you guys are the greatest friends
a giant doofus could have.

04:58.564 --> 05:01.032
Good Lord!
Brought down by one beer?

05:01.134 --> 05:03.534
And a couple of these babies.

05:03.636 --> 05:07.970
Now, if you'll excuse me,
I'm off to the barn dance.

05:09.208 --> 05:12.177
<i>Watch his head.</i>

05:15.381 --> 05:17.906
Where am I?

05:18.017 --> 05:20.485
Oh, they don't want me anymore.

05:24.891 --> 05:28.190
<i># Paul was just as lonely</i>
<i>as a man could get #</i>

05:28.294 --> 05:32.788
