And now-

05:35.001 --> 05:38.562
Oh, boy.
I wish you were real.

05:38.671 --> 05:42.107
Mmm.

05:50.550 --> 05:52.450
Hey, what the-

05:52.518 --> 05:54.486
Oh, it's a miracle!

05:54.587 --> 05:57.556
I'll call you Babe.
You'll be my best friend.

06:03.996 --> 06:05.964
<i>So Paul and his blue ox Babe...</i>

06:06.065 --> 06:10.001
<i>traveled all across this great land,</i>
<i>leavin'their mark.</i>

06:27.420 --> 06:30.981
<i>Excuse me. Paul Bunyan</i>
<i>never fought Rodan.</i>

06:31.090 --> 06:33.957
