really inconsistent.

06:34.060 --> 06:36.358
I mean, one minute,
he's 10 feet tall.

06:36.462 --> 06:38.760
The next,
his feet are as big as a lake.

06:38.865 --> 06:42.266
- Hey, hey, hey! Who's the hobo here?
- I'm just sayin'.

06:45.471 --> 06:48.929
