- Oh.

07:32.685 --> 07:35.586
Whoo-hoo!

07:45.031 --> 07:46.931
Mmm!

07:54.941 --> 07:57.808
Oh!

07:59.879 --> 08:03.815
We've been together a long time now.

08:03.916 --> 08:07.682
- When are we gonna, you know-
- Soon.

08:07.787 --> 08:11.382
I just need a few more yoga classes.
Oh, look!

08:11.491 --> 08:13.516
A shooting star.

08:13.626 --> 08:17.289
<i>Hey, that meteor's</i>
<i>headed straight for us...</i>

08:17.396 --> 08:20.763
