to show us his love.

08:27.273 --> 08:30.504
No! We're gonna die!

08:30.610 --> 08:33.203
There's only one man
who can save us.

08:33.312 --> 08:35.212
Oh, I get it.

08:35.313 --> 08:37.544
When I'm crushing and killing you,
you don't like me.

08:37.650 --> 08:41.211
But when I can save your life,
suddenly I'm Mr. Popular.

08:41.320 --> 08:42.844
Yeah. That's pretty much it.

08:42.955 --> 08:44.855
Whoo-hoo!
I'm Mr. Popular!

08:53.132 --> 08:55.157
Come on.
Right across the plate.

08:55.268 --> 08:57.168
Let's see what you got, huh?

08:57.270 --> 09:00.831
This one's for the little crippled boy...
that I crippled.

09:00.940 --> 09:02.840
You can do it, Paul!

09:02.942 --> 09:05.604
Gimme a kiss for luck.

09:05.711 --> 09:07.440
Ow! Hot!

09:07.547 --> 09:09.947
Oh, boy, that's-

09:10.049 --> 09:12.483
Oh, come on!
Ow!

09:20.760 --> 09:25.720
<i>And that's how Paul Bunyan</i>
<i>started the great Chicago fire.</i>

09:25.831 --> 09:27.958
Boy, that story had everything.

09:28.067 --> 09:31.298
- A giant, house crushing, a meteor-
- Townspeople.

09:31.404 --> 09:33.304
Got any more tall tales?

09:33.406 --> 09:36.341
Well, I suppose I could
spin ya a few more yarns.

09:36.442 --> 09:40.742
But first, who wants to give
me a sponge bath? I'm filthy.

09:42.915 --> 09:44.815
All right.
But your next story...

09:44.917 --> 09:46.885
better be worth it.

09:49.322 --> 09:51.222
Get in there good.

09:51.324 --> 09:53.690
Yeah, that's it.
Don't be shy.

09:53.793 --> 09:55.818
There you go.

09:59.065 --> 10:01.659
<i>Okay. Ready for another impression?</i>

