18:13.859 --> 18:16.953
- That will be two cents, boys.
- Two cents?

18:17.062 --> 18:20.725
Hey, if you think my prices are high,
go across the street.

18:22.935 --> 18:24.800
<i>Thank you. Come again.</i>

18:24.903 --> 18:28.600
- He put the lard pone on top of the egg pone.
- Dang!

18:31.110 --> 18:32.577
Double dang!

18:35.080 --> 18:37.378
Aw, donkey butter!

18:43.322 --> 18:46.553
Oh, it's no use.

18:46.658 --> 18:49.252
I got an idea.

18:50.829 --> 18:53.024
Uh- Hmm.

18:53.132 --> 18:56.465
Well, dog my cats.
